  "project_objectives": "This brand health tracking study measures brand awareness, perceptions, purchase behavior, and competitive position for Acme Strawberries against six competitor brands in the fresh strawberry market. Key metrics include unaided/aided brand awareness, brand purchase history, 11-attribute brand evaluation (5-point Likert), purchase intent, category and Acme purchase frequency, last brand purchased, NPS, and brand preference. N=800 fresh strawberry purchasers in past 6 months.",
